gco:CharacterString.#text: Coal zone boundary for the Mannville Coal Zone is based on subcrops generated by Alberta Geological Survey Special Report 007 (Regional Evaluation of the Coalbed Methane Potential in the Plains and Foothills of Alberta, Stratigraphy and Rank Study). We used additional coal picks from various sources to refine the boundary.

gmd:LocalisedCharacterString.#text:
La limite de la zone de charbon de la zone de charbon de Mannville est fondée sur les sous-cultures générées par le rapport spécial 007 de l'Alberta Geological Survey (Regional Evaluation of the Coalbed Methane Potential in the Plains and Foothills of Alberta, Stratigraphy and Rank Study). Nous avons utilisé d'autres pics de charbon provenant de diverses sources pour affiner la frontière.
